Package task

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildTask
    BuildTask is a Task in which a Drone is assigned a Building to build.
    ChargeTask
    ChargeTask is a Task that assigns a Drone to find a SolarPlant and recharge.
    DeadTask
    DeadTask is a Task that removes a Drone from all the acting Drones.
    DefaultTask
    DefaultTask is a Task for Drones idling.
    DepositTask
    DepositTask is a Task in which a Drone deposits resources into a Building.
    ItemBuildTask
    ItemBuiltTask is a Task in which an Items is built and given to a Drone.
    MethaneTask
    MethaneTask is a Task that assigns a Drone to find a MethanePlant and refuel.
    MoveTask
    MoveTask is a Task in which a Drone generates a new path to a location and moves there.
    RepairTask
    RepairTask is a Task that assigns a Drone to find a Engineering and repair.
    Task
    Task is the abstract class representing different behaviors and commands that are issuable to a Drone.
    WaitTask
    WaitTask is a Task in which a Task in which a Drone sits in one place.
